				<div class="lockerrooom-entry-title">
					Football <span class="by">by</span> Brady Poppinga
					<div class="author-image" style="background-image: url(https://s3.amazonaws.com/footballbyfootball-dev/Headshots/pro_bradypoppinga.jpg)"></div>
